{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/selector-no-vendor-prefix/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/selector-no-type/","description":"selector-no-universal Deprecated: Instead use the selector-max-universal rule with 0 as its primary option. Disallow the universal…","title":"selector-no-universal"},"body":"<h1 id=\"selector-no-universal\"><a href=\"#selector-no-universal\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>selector-no-universal</h1>\n<p><strong><em>Deprecated: Instead use the <a href=\"../selector-max-universal/\"><code>selector-max-universal</code></a> rule with <code>0</code> as its primary option.</em></strong></p>\n<p>Disallow the universal selector.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">    * {}\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/** ↑\n * This selector */</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Options</h2>\n<h3 id=\"true\"><a href=\"#true\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>true</code></h3>\n<p>The following patterns are considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\">* {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\">*, <span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\">* > <span class=\"hljs-selector-attr\">[foo]</span> {}</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.foo</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-attr\">[foo]</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#foo</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.bar</span> > <span class=\"hljs-selector-id\">#foo</span> {}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/selector-no-universal.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/selector-no-universal/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-no-universal/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-no-universal/index.html.2a07182e1f59d6883ed942a505f4f577.json"}